ct-link\" href=\"/service?target-customer=city#service-search-result\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-city.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-city@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"product-link__text\">市町村</span></a></li>\n          <li class=\"product-list__item\"> <a class=\"product-link\" href=\"/service?target-customer=medical-institution#service-search-result\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-medical-institution.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-medical-institution@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"product-link__text\">医療機関</span></a></li>\n          <li class=\"product-list__item\"> <a class=\"product-link\" href=\"/service?target-customer=company-organization#service-search-result\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-company-organization.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-company-organization@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"product-link__text\">企業・団体</span></a></li>\n          <li class=\"product-list__item\"> <a class=\"product-link\" href=\"/service?target-customer=educational-institution#service-search-result\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-educational-institution.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-educational-institution@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"product-link__text\">教育機関</span></a></li>\n          <li class=\"product-list__item\"> <a class=\"product-link\" href=\"/service?target-customer=outsourcing-cloud#service-search-result\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-outsourcing-cloud.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-forte-outsourcing-cloud@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"product-link__text\">アウトソーシング<span class=\"d-inline-block\">・クラウド</span></span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p class=\"home-section-more\"> <a class=\"dot-button\" href=\"/company/forte\">ICSの強み</a></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"home-section home-section--datacenter\"> \n    <div class=\"home-section-inner\">\n      <div class=\"home-section-inner__image\">\n        <div class=\"home-section-image home-section-image--datacenter scroll-animation scroll-animation--slide-in-down\"></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"home-section-inner__body\">\n        <h2 class=\"lead-heading\"> <span class=\"d-xl-block\">信頼性の高いファシリティと</span><span class=\"d-xl-block\">堅牢なセキュリティで</span><span class=\"d-xl-block\">高品質なサービスを提供する</span>データセンター</h2>\n        <p class=\"home-section-text\">\n            各種設備面やセキュリティ対策面について、大幅に充実強化したデータセンターを整備いたしました。<br>これまで以上にお客様の情報資産のセキュリティ向上と事業継続性の確保を強力にご支援します。<br>また、システムのクラウド化、DX(デジタルトランスフォーメーション)の加速やデータセンターの地方分散への気運の高まりもあり、ますます多様化するデータセンターニーズに柔軟に対応していきます。</p>\n        <p class=\"home-section-more\"> <a class=\"dot-button\" href=\"/company/datacenter\">データセンター</a></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"home-section home-section--package-system\"> \n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"package-system-inner\">\n        <div class=\"package-system-box scroll-animation scroll-animation--slide-in-right\">\n          <h2 class=\"lead-heading\"> <span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">全国に広がる</span><span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">アイシーエスの</span>ユーザ</h2>\n                      <p class=\"package-system-used\"> <span class=\"package-system-used__number\">14</span>県<span class=\"package-system-used__number\">197</span>市町村<span class=\"package-system-used__number\">53</span>医療機関</p>\n                  </div>\n        <picture class=\"package-system-prefecture\"> \n          <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-package-system-prefecture-pc.svg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/home/img-package-system-prefecture-sp.svg\" alt=\"北海道、東北